{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[Ab]  Oh, who knows how long this will last
[Db]  Now we've come so far, so fast
[Ab]  But somewhere back there in the dust
That[Db]  same small town in each[Eb]  of us
[Ab]  I need to remember this
[Db]  So baby, give me just one kiss
[Ab]  And let me take a long last look
Be[Fm]fore we say[Db]  goodbye[Eb]
{end_of_verse}


